            "title": "A股向下   低開後跌幅擴大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段向下，低開後跌幅擴大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3634，跌5點或0.14%，現報3629，跌10點, 0.28%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報11136，跌57點或0.19%，現報11116，跌41點或0.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報4019，跌5點或0.12%，現報4104，跌9點或0.24%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2338，跌5點或0.21%，現報2336，跌6點或0.29%。</p>\n</div>",
