            "title": "港股開跌113點  中芯及生科股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌113點，報24968點，恒生科技指數跌45點或0.83%，報5500點 ; 恒生國企指數開跌49點或0.55%，報8932點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交25.29億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)績後受壓，開跌3.77%，報51元 ; 華虹(01347)升0.49%，報45元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">再鼎醫藥(09688)瀉10.01%，報27.34元，中期虧損收窄至8917萬美元。藥明康德(02359)跌2.15%，報97.95元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015)升0.26%，報96.7元; 寧德時代(03750)升1.24%，報407元。</p>\n</div>",
